{"tid":1920013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與台交往遭恐嚇 捷克總理要求中國換大使","createTime":"2020-03-11T07:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T09:35:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3bfcf60b3ccf7933d94c792202d6fcfe0bac34","tid":1920013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200311/56JFGEVBQALOCAGSQONP3FLPXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200311%2F56JFGEVBQALOCAGSQONP3FLPXI%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0sttVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=53934495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200311%2F56JFGEVBQALOCAGSQONP3FLPXI%2F&h=6d110c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200311/56JFGEVBQALOCAGSQONP3FLPXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n與台交往遭恐嚇<br />\n捷克總理要求中國換大使<br />\n<br />\n中國外交官咄咄逼人的「戰狼」作風，經常被指破壞兩國關係。中國駐布拉格大使日前公開威脅捷克，若參議院院長一旦訪問台灣，中國將報復捷克企業，事件引發捷克政壇不滿，捷克總理巴比斯（Andrej Babis）亦表態支持參議員要求中國撤換駐捷克大使。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583857724_764f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583857724_764f.jpg&h=beeba2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國駐捷克大使張建敏。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐布拉格大使張建敏在今年1月致函捷克總統辦公室，稱若捷克資深議員訪台，「那些與中國有經濟利益關係的捷克企業將付出代價」，信中還列舉數間捷克在華公司，如捷克汽車製造商斯柯達（Skoda Auto）、樂器製造商佩卓夫（Petrof）鋼琴、金融企業捷信集團（Home Credit）等。信中的「資深議員」，外界相信是時任參議院議長柯佳洛（Jaroslav Kubera）。他本擬在2月訪台，不料在一月下旬病故。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583857723_f9bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583857723_f9bb.jpg&h=0ea1cb80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捷克總理巴比斯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捷克本周商討外交政策<br />\n<br />\n現參議院議長維特齊（Milos Vystrcil）稱欲要求中國撤換駐布拉格大使，當地電視稱巴比斯亦接納維特齊建議，他稱：「他所寫的信完全不能接受，我們必須拒絕。」據悉，包括總統澤曼（Milos Zeman）在內四名捷克高官，將於本周三商討捷克外交政策，相信他們會處理這一問題。近年來，澤曼算是「親中派」，一直希望修補中捷關係。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部發言人稱，巴比斯支持撤換大使，顯示中國透過「一帶一路」威脅政府勿與台灣交往，這種操作已引起捷克政府與民眾普遍反感。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"5f7b972f2a8ba32a8271e8f5b4cce7a05093b043","tid":1920013,"uid":253978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"支共全盛時期可以得罪幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1c372ad12a48974089ca3b12c091949b68a76e","tid":1920013,"uid":40267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"狗換幾多隻都係狗嚟ga la"},{"pid":"fa06244c785366cff28dceb55c9f9ab86cf3c7bd","tid":1920013,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"隔離隻大使啦"},{"pid":"52ed7559cfacf420dafb80301b19c7abd3dfb63a","tid":1920013,"uid":99827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f7b972f2a8ba32a8271e8f5b4cce7a05093b043","tid":1920013,"uid":253978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"支共全盛時期可以得罪幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"不如問而家有邊個國家唔憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58348aab842d0fbc103fa6faab9d5368f30ebd50","tid":1920013,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"真係柒出國際"},{"pid":"b132596de81c7f6eed0facd633c93fb7ef53ce05","tid":1920013,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"相信中國駐布拉格大使感染Wu Flu<br />\n捷克當局應該盡快隔離呢位大使, 幫佢打特效藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45d04e5f25406b4398279a5e17aea62b29fdeaf","tid":1920013,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"個外交官咪又係聽中央政府支笛<br />\n需要做嘅係驅逐大使 斷外交關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個總理都肯定知嘅  所謂要求換大使只係表達不滿嘅手段<br />\n但對住個流氓政權肯定唔會work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a046fd7be74c4513be871d205d8a3146ff097b2e","tid":1920013,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"中國駐布拉格大使日前公開威脅捷克<br />\n<br />\n又唔見對美帝咁大聲"},{"pid":"2302091a3d15a60fe4c18c6536df7686bf9aff50","tid":1920013,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"信中的「資深議員」，外界相信是時任參議院議長柯佳洛（Jaroslav Kubera）。他本擬在2月訪台，不料在一月下旬病故。<br />\n<br />\n我強烈建議捷克當局搵驗屍專家高手去睇下係咪死於生病<br />\n定係某D 支式國度係度做衰野"},{"pid":"59a309c74aed38182622b16c5f315f39020f1b41","tid":1920013,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52ed7559cfacf420dafb80301b19c7abd3dfb63a","tid":1920013,"uid":99827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f7b972f2a8ba32a8271e8f5b4cce7a05093b043","tid":1920013,"uid":253978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"支共全盛時期可以得罪幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"不如問而家有邊個國家唔憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伊朗都應該開始憎憎地佢"},{"pid":"d4963648a1f9dc8dedba68bbf9c3a0463b7a7f8a","tid":1920013,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"直接驅逐啦"},{"pid":"951630fdd650ef38095f3e12554cf881ec06eb44","tid":1920013,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-ur